text = "This demo scene is set up to show how the Reader can swap between conversations at runtime.
The Reader starts off with the simple greeting but pressing any of the buttons at the bottom of the scene will change the current conversation.
Give it a go and be sure to look at the script attached to the reader node to see how it works!"
